          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800">Interactive Recipe Adjuster</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">A dynamic web app that lets users adjust recipe quantities based on serving sizes, offering a tailored cooking experience.</p>
